# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
## [3.0.1] - 2022-10-31
### Added
- Fix some minor bugs
## [3.0.0] - 2024-09-20
### Added
 - Migrate from v13 to v17 of angular
 - Add prefix
 - Make compatible with template driven forms
 - Add forRoot or forChild configuration
 - Works without translations configuration
## [2.2.1] - 2022-08-16
### Added
- Fix message when language change
## [2.2.0] - 2022-05-30
### Added
- Code optimization adding internal pipe to manage message
## [2.1.0] - 2022-01-21
### Added
- Upgrade to angular 13
- Code optimization
## [2.0.2] - 2021-03-26
### Added
- Update documentation
- Code optimization

## [2.0.1] - 2021-03-24
### Added
- Upgrade to angular 11
- Code optimization

## [2.0.0] - 2021-03-22
### Added
- Update coverage to ngx-error-message
- Change the directive call
- Improvements in some default validations
- Code optimization

## [1.3.0] - 2020-11-07
### Added
- Complete coverage to ngx-error-message
- Add pipeline
- Code optimization

## [1.2.1] - 2020-06-04
### Added
- Add coverage to ngx-error-message

## [1.2.0] - 2020-05-29
### Added
